snippet.title: Is Amber Liu cancelled?
snippet.description:
The full video of the man and the cop: https://twitter.com/keilobenjamin/status/1193163017069838337?s=21

This is an important issue to talk about, I’m sorry if u guys were expecting a koreaboo video but I enjoy reporting on Kpop news, if u guys want me to do more videos where I gather up info and show peoples opinions let me know, I think making videos like this are so interesting! I hope that doesn’t come off weird lol
